### =================
### PERFORMANCE CONTROLLER TESTS
### =================

### 1. Create a performance record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutLogId": 1,
  "setNumber": 1,
  "reps": 12,
  "weight": 50.5,
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "durationSeconds": 1800.0,
  "distanceKm": 5.0,
  "caloriesBurned": 300,
  "notes": "Good form maintained throughout"
}

### 2. Get all performance records for user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 3. Get performance records by workout log ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/performance/workout-log/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 4. Get performance records by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/performance?startDate=2024-06-01&endDate=2024-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 5. Update a performance record
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/performance/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutLogId": 1,
  "setNumber": 1,
  "reps": 15,
  "weight": 55.0,
  "durationMinutes": 32,
  "durationSeconds": 1920.0,
  "distanceKm": 5.2,
  "caloriesBurned": 320,
  "notes": "Improved performance, increased weight"
}

### 6. Delete a performance record
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/performance/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}